<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>HOME | DNA PPS — Planejamento Patrimonial e Sucessório</title>
<meta name="description" content="O Inventário é um problema e a DNA PPS pode evitá-lo. Planejamento Patrimonial e Sucessório para proteger seu patrimônio e reduzir custos." />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Wix+Madefor+Display:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Wix+Madefor+Text:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
/* =========================================================================
   DNA PPS — Reconstrução fiel da LP (fora do Wix)
   Única mudança funcional vs. site atual: seção de simulação => calculadora ITCMD interativa
   ========================================================================= */
:root{
  --dark:#1b1a16;
  --darker:#070709;
  --ouro:#d9b44a;
  --peri-1:#2e3e72; --peri-2:#4954d8; --peri-3:#6573ee;
  --txt:#ffffff;
  --display:"Wix Madefor Display","Helvetica Neue",Arial,sans-serif;
  --text:"Wix Madefor Text","Helvetica Neue",Arial,sans-serif;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{font-family:var(--text);color:var(--txt);background:var(--darker);-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;overflow-x:hidden}
img{max-width:100%;display:block}
a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}
.wrap{max-width:1200px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 clamp(20px,5vw,64px)}
h1,h2,h3{font-family:var(--display);font-weight:400;line-height:1.15;letter-spacing:-.01em}

/* ---------- Botão pílula contornado ---------- */
.btn{
  display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:28px;justify-content:space-between;
  border:1.6px solid rgba(255,255,255,.92);border-radius:50px;
  padding:15px 30px;font-family:var(--text);font-size:.94rem;color:#fff;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,.08);cursor:pointer;transition:.22s;min-width:230px;
}
.btn:hover{background:#fff;color:var(--dark);border-color:#fff;transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,.28)}
.btn.cta{background:#fff;color:var(--dark);border-color:#fff;font-weight:600}
.btn.cta:hover{background:var(--ouro);border-color:var(--ouro);color:#1a1530}
.btn svg{width:34px;height:12px;flex:none}
.btn.dark{border-color:rgba(0,0,0,.5);color:#1b1a16}
.btn.dark:hover{background:#1b1a16;color:#fff;border-color:#1b1a16}

/* ---------- Header ---------- */
header{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;width:100%;z-index:50;background:rgba(27,26,22,.97);backdrop-filter:blur(6px)}
.hd{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:24px;min-height:74px}
.nav{display:flex;gap:30px}
.nav a{font-size:.74rem;letter-spacing:.12em;text-transform:uppercase;opacity:.92;transition:.2s}
.nav a:hover{color:var(--ouro)}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px}
.brand img{height:46px;width:auto;border-radius:3px}
.brand .bt{font-family:var(--display);font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.15;font-weight:500}
.burger{display:none;background:none;border:0;color:#fff;font-size:1.6rem;cursor:pointer}

/* ---------- Hero ---------- */
.hero{position:relative;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;overflow:hidden}
.hero video,.hero .poster{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;z-index:0}
.hero::after{content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;z-index:1;
  background:linear-gradient(180deg,rgba(15,14,12,.55) 0%,rgba(15,14,12,.25) 45%,rgba(15,14,12,.85) 100%)}
.hero .wrap{position:relative;z-index:2;padding-bottom:clamp(70px,11vh,130px);width:100%;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;text-align:center}
.hero h1{font-size:clamp(2.1rem,4.6vw,3.6rem);max-width:none;margin-bottom:24px;line-height:1.18}
.hero p{font-size:clamp(1rem,1.5vw,1.2rem);max-width:64ch;color:rgba(255,255,255,.9);margin-bottom:32px;line-height:1.6}

/* ---------- Bloco texto+mídia (seções marrom) ---------- */
.warm{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#17110b 0%,#3d2a1c 22%,#7d5641 45%,#9b705d 58%,#5f4030 80%,#221710 100%)}
.media-row{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:clamp(30px,6vw,90px);align-items:center;padding:clamp(50px,8vw,100px) 0}
.media-row .media{border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 30px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.45);aspect-ratio:16/11;background:#000}
.media-row .media video,.media-row .media img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.media-row h2{font-size:clamp(1.9rem,3.4vw,2.4rem);margin-bottom:20px}
.media-row p{font-size:1.05rem;line-height:1.7;color:rgba(255,255,255,.9);margin-bottom:26px}
.media-row.rev .media{order:2}

/* ---------- Pilares ---------- */
.dark-sec{background:var(--darker);padding:clamp(60px,9vw,120px) 0}
.pilares{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr 1fr;gap:60px;align-items:center}
.pilares h2{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4.6vw,3.6rem);margin-bottom:36px}
.pilares ul{list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:26px}
.pilares li{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:20px;font-size:1.15rem}
.pilares li svg.pic{width:42px;height:16px;flex:none;fill:var(--ouro)}
.pilares .vid{border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;aspect-ratio:1/1;background:#000;box-shadow:0 30px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}
.pilares .vid video,.pilares .vid img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}

/* ---------- Soluções (6 cards) ---------- */
.sol-head{text-align:center;margin-bottom:50px}
.sol-head h2{font-size:clamp(2.4rem,5vw,4.2rem)}
.sol-head .div{width:46px;height:2px;background:var(--ouro);margin:20px auto 0}
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.12);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.12);border-radius:10px;overflow:hidden}
.card{background:var(--darker);padding:40px 38px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:26px;align-items:center;min-height:190px}
.card .ctx{flex:1}
.card h3{font-style:italic;font-weight:400;font-size:clamp(1.55rem,2.7vw,2.2rem);margin-bottom:14px;color:#fff}
.card p{font-size:.95rem;line-height:1.6;color:rgba(255,255,255,.72);max-width:42ch}
.card .cic{width:76px;height:76px;flex:none;color:rgba(255,255,255,.8);fill:currentColor}
.card .cic.stroke{fill:none;stroke:currentColor;stroke-width:3.4}

/* ---------- Simulação / Calculadora (periwinkle) ---------- */
#solucoes{background:#0e1228}
.sim{background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--peri-1) 0%,var(--peri-2) 50%,var(--peri-3) 100%);padding:clamp(56px,8vw,104px) 0}
.sim>.wrap{max-width:1080px}
.sim .sim-title{text-align:center;max-width:none;margin:0 auto clamp(30px,5vw,46px);font-size:clamp(2.05rem,4.3vw,3.35rem);letter-spacing:.004em}
.calc-form{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.2fr 1fr 1.2fr;gap:16px;max-width:900px;margin:0 auto clamp(22px,3.5vw,32px)}
.fld{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;text-align:left}
.fld label{font-size:.82rem;font-weight:500;color:rgba(255,255,255,.92)}
.fld label small{display:block;font-weight:400;font-size:.72rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.62);margin-top:2px}
.fld input,.fld select{width:100%;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.28);border-radius:12px;padding:14px 16px;color:#fff;font-family:var(--text);font-size:1rem;font-weight:500;outline:none;transition:.18s}
.fld input::placeholder{color:rgba(255,255,255,.5);font-weight:400}
.fld input:focus,.fld select:focus{border-color:var(--ouro);background:rgba(255,255,255,.16)}
.fld select{appearance:none;cursor:pointer;background-image:url("data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='14' height='14' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' stroke='%23ffffff' stroke-width='2.5'><path d='M6 9l6 6 6-6'/></svg>");background-repeat:no-repeat;background-position:right 14px center;padding-right:42px}
.fld select option{color:#1a1a1a}
.calc-result{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;border-radius:18px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 24px 60px rgba(0,0,0,.3);max-width:900px;margin:0 auto}
.col-head{background:#0b0b0d;color:var(--ouro);text-align:center;font-weight:600;font-size:1.02rem;padding:18px 14px}
.col-body{padding:26px 22px 30px;min-height:250px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px}
.col-inv .col-body{background:linear-gradient(180deg,#7d7d80,#6c6c70);color:#fff}
.col-plan .col-body{background:#f3f3f5;color:#2b2b2b}
.line{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:3px}
.line .k{font-size:.8rem;opacity:.85}
.line .v{font-size:1.06rem;font-weight:600}
.col-plan .line .v{color:#13693c}
.dv{height:1px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.22);margin:2px 0}
.col-plan .dv{background:rgba(0,0,0,.1)}
.tot{margin-top:auto}
.tot .k{font-size:.84rem;opacity:.9;font-weight:500}
.tot .v{font-size:1.5rem;font-weight:700}
.col-inv .tot .v{color:#fff}.col-plan .tot .v{color:#0f7a43}
.eco{max-width:900px;margin:22px auto 0;background:rgba(255,255,255,.1);border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.22);border-radius:16px;padding:20px 24px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:18px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.eco .lbl{font-size:.95rem;font-weight:500;color:rgba(255,255,255,.88)}
.eco .big{font-size:clamp(1.5rem,3vw,2.1rem);font-weight:700;color:var(--ouro)}
.eco .pct{font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.7)}
.sim-disc{max-width:900px;margin:18px auto 0;font-size:.76rem;line-height:1.55;color:rgba(255,255,255,.62);text-align:center}
.sim-cta{text-align:center;margin-top:30px}

/* ---------- Quem somos ---------- */
.quem{text-align:center;max-width:880px;margin:0 auto}
.quem h2{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4.5vw,3.5rem);margin-bottom:26px;order:-1}
.quem p{font-size:1.08rem;line-height:1.8;color:rgba(255,255,255,.82)}

/* ---------- Diretores ---------- */
.dirs{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:30px;max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto}
.dir{text-align:center}
.dir img{width:100%;aspect-ratio:317/408;object-fit:cover;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:18px;filter:grayscale(.1)}
.dir h3{font-size:1.38rem;margin-bottom:4px}
.dir p{font-size:.9rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6)}

/* ---------- Parceiros ---------- */
.parc{text-align:center}
.parc h3{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.4vw,3rem);margin-bottom:26px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85)}
.parc img{height:84px;width:auto;margin:0 auto;opacity:.95}

/* ---------- Form ---------- */
.formsec{background:#fff;color:#1b1a16;padding:clamp(60px,8vw,110px) 0}
.formgrid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:clamp(30px,6vw,80px);align-items:center}
.formgrid h2{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,4.6vw,3.6rem);margin-bottom:16px;color:#1b1a16}
.formgrid p{color:#555;font-size:1.05rem}
.lead-form{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px;background:#13132a;padding:34px;border-radius:14px}
.lead-form .ff{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px}
.lead-form label{font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85)}
.lead-form input{padding:13px 15px;border-radius:9px;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.18);background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);color:#fff;font-family:var(--text);font-size:1rem;outline:none}
.lead-form input:focus{border-color:var(--peri-3)}
.lead-form button{margin-top:6px;padding:14px;border:0;border-radius:9px;background:#3b41d6;color:#fff;font-family:var(--text);font-size:1rem;font-weight:600;cursor:pointer;transition:.2s}
.lead-form button:hover{background:#2c32c4}
.lead-form .ok{display:none;color:#7ee2a8;font-size:.95rem;text-align:center;padding:8px}

/* ---------- Footer ---------- */
footer{background:#0c0d11;padding:clamp(50px,7vw,90px) 0 40px}
.ft-logo{font-family:var(--display);font-size:2.4rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.05em;margin-bottom:26px}
.ft-mail{font-size:1rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);margin-bottom:18px}
.ft-mail a{color:var(--ouro)}
.ft-social{display:flex;gap:16px;margin-bottom:26px}
.ft-social a{width:40px;height:40px;display:grid;place-items:center;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border-radius:50%;transition:.2s}
.ft-social a:hover{background:rgba(255,255,255,.16)}
.ft-social img{width:20px;height:20px}
.ft-addr{font-size:.92rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);margin-bottom:30px;max-width:50ch}
.ft-bottom{border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);padding-top:24px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;font-size:.85rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55)}
.ft-bottom .links{display:flex;gap:24px}

/* ---------- WhatsApp flutuante ---------- */
.wa{position:fixed;right:22px;bottom:22px;z-index:60;width:58px;height:58px;border-radius:50%;background:#25d366;display:grid;place-items:center;box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.3);transition:.2s}
.wa:hover{transform:scale(1.06)}
.wa svg{width:32px;height:32px;fill:#fff}
/* ── POPUP QUALIFICAÇÃO ── */
#qpopup{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(0,0,0,.78);z-index:9999;display:none;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:16px}
#qpopup.open{display:flex}
.qcard{background:#1b1a16;border:1px solid rgba(217,180,74,.25);border-radius:14px;width:100%;max-width:470px;padding:36px 32px;position:relative;max-height:90vh;overflow-y:auto}
@media(max-width:480px){.qcard{padding:28px 20px}}
.qclose{position:absolute;top:14px;right:18px;background:none;border:none;color:rgba(255,255,255,.45);font-size:26px;line-height:1;cursor:pointer;padding:0}
.qclose:hover{color:#fff}
.qcard h3{font-family:'Wix Madefor Display',sans-serif;font-size:21px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin:0 0 6px}
.qcard>div>p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);font-size:14px;margin:0 0 22px}
.qfield{margin-bottom:15px}
.qfield label{display:block;font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:rgba(255,255,255,.65);margin-bottom:5px;letter-spacing:.03em}
.qfield input[type=text],.qfield input[type=email],.qfield input[type=tel],.qfield input:not([type]){width:100%;box-sizing:border-box;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13);border-radius:8px;color:#fff;font-size:15px;padding:11px 14px;outline:none;transition:border-color .2s;font-family:inherit}
.qfield input:focus{border-color:var(--ouro)}
.qfield input.err{border-color:#e05252}
.qradio-group{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:2px}
.qrlabel{cursor:pointer;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.13);border-radius:8px;padding:10px 14px;font-size:13.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.75);transition:all .18s;user-select:none}
.qrlabel input[type=radio]{display:none}
.qrlabel.sel{background:rgba(217,180,74,.14);border-color:var(--ouro);color:var(--ouro);font-weight:600}
.qerr{color:#e05252;font-size:12.5px;margin-top:4px;display:none}
.qsubmit{width:100%;background:var(--ouro);color:#1b1a16;border:none;border-radius:8px;font-size:16px;font-weight:700;padding:14px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:10px;transition:opacity .2s;font-family:'Wix Madefor Display',sans-serif;letter-spacing:.01em}
.qsubmit:hover{opacity:.88}
.qsubmit:disabled{opacity:.45;cursor:not-allowed}
.qthanks{display:none;text-align:center;padding:20px 0 8px}
.qthanks .qti{font-size:42px;margin-bottom:14px}
.qthanks h4{font-size:20px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;margin:0 0 8px;font-family:'Wix Madefor Display',sans-serif}
.qthanks p{color:rgba(255,255,255,.6);font-size:15px;margin:0 0 20px;line-height:1.5}
.qthanks .qebookbtn{display:inline-block;background:var(--ouro);color:#1b1a16;border-radius:8px;padding:13px 28px;font-weight:700;font-size:15px;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Wix Madefor Display',sans-serif;margin-bottom:14px}
.qthanks .qebookbtn:hover{opacity:.88}
.qthanks .qfechar{display:block;font-size:13px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.35);cursor:pointer;text-decoration:none;margin-top:4px}

/* ---------- Animações de reveal no scroll (estilo Wix) ---------- */
.reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(34px);transition:opacity .85s cubic-bezier(.2,.6,.2,1),transform .85s cubic-bezier(.2,.6,.2,1)}
.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}
.hero video{transition:transform .1s linear}
@media (prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.reveal{opacity:1!important;transform:none!important;transition:none}}

/* ---------- Responsivo ---------- */
@media (max-width:860px){
  .nav{display:none}
  .burger{display:block}
  .media-row,.pilares,.cards,.formgrid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .media-row.rev .media{order:0}
  .calc-form{grid-template-columns:1fr;max-width:440px}
  .calc-result{grid-template-columns:1fr;max-width:440px}
  .col-inv{order:1}.col-plan{order:2}
  .dirs{grid-template-columns:1fr;max-width:360px}
  .eco{flex-direction:column;text-align:center;gap:6px}
  .brand .bt{display:none}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
<noscript><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-5CNV4XH5"
height="0" width="0" style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript>
<!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->

<!-- ===================== HEADER ===================== -->
<header>
  <div class="wrap hd">
    <nav class="nav">
      <a href="#topo">PLANEJAMENTO</a>
      <a href="#solucoes">SOLUÇÕES</a>
      <a href="#simulacao">SIMULAÇÃO</a>
      <a href="#contato">CONTATOS</a>
    </nav>
    <div class="brand">
      <img src="assets/logo-dna.jpeg" alt="DNA PPS" />
      <div class="bt">Planejamento Patrimonial<br>e Sucessório</div>
    </div>
    <button class="burger" aria-label="Menu" onclick="document.querySelector('.nav').style.display=(getComputedStyle(document.querySelector('.nav')).display==='none'?'flex':'none')">☰</button>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- ===================== HERO ===================== -->
<section class="hero" id="topo">
  <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="assets/hero-poster.jpg">
    <source src="assets/hero.mp4" type="video/mp4">
  </video>
  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>O Inventário é um problema e a DNA PPS pode evitá-lo</h1>
    <p>Perder um ente querido nunca é fácil, o que fica ainda mais delicado por conta dos altos custos para a transmissão da herança e possíveis conflitos na partilha dos bens.</p>
    <a class="btn" href="#tributacao">Atenção para mudanças no imposto sobre a morte
      <svg viewBox="0 0 40 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M0 6h38M32 1l6 5-6 5"/></svg></a>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ===================== SEÇÕES MARROM (mídia + texto) ===================== -->
<section class="warm">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="media-row">
      <div class="media">
        <video autoplay muted loop playsinline poster="assets/hero-poster.jpg">
          <source src="assets/video-planejamento.mp4" type="video/mp4"></video>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Planejamento Patrimonial e Sucessório.</h2>
        <p>Através da análise de especialistas, iremos avaliar a alocação do seu patrimônio buscando aplicar medidas que irão evitar as consequências negativas de um inventário.</p>
        <a class="btn" href="#consultores">Consultores
          <svg viewBox="0 0 40 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M0 6h38M32 1l6 5-6 5"/></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="media-row rev" id="tributacao">
      <div class="media" style="aspect-ratio:512/500;background:#e9e4da">
        <img src="assets/leao-receita.webp" alt="Atenção à tributação sobre o inventário" style="object-fit:contain">
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Atenção para mudanças na tributação sobre o inventário.</h2>
        <p>Na busca por evitar o inventário, recomendamos urgência na avaliação do tema. Com o advento da reforma tributária (Emenda Constitucional nº. 132 de dezembro de 2023), a tendência é que o imposto sobre a morte (ITCMD ou ITCD) seja alterado, em muitos estados, para a sua alíquota máxima no percentual 8% sobre o valor da herança. Neste cenário, o ano de 2024 é crucial para esse assunto, visto que, a partir de 2025, os contribuintes poderão enfrentar uma alíquota dobrada na realização dos inventários e na doação de bens.</p>
        <p style="margin-top:14px">Não bastasse isto, o inventário também tem outros elevados custos como o ganho de capital do espólio (15% a 22,5% sobre a diferença entre o valor de declaração ao IR e o valor de mercado do patrimônio), às custas judiciais/cartórios e os honorários advocatícios (10% sobre valor da herança).</p>
        <a class="btn" href="#consultores" style="margin-top:24px">Consultores
          <svg viewBox="0 0 40 12" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.4"><path d="M0 6h38M32 1l6 5-6 5"/></svg></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

